claim: Queen Victoria's son belonged to a house.
premise_source_doc_sentence: (  Other members of the House of Glücksburg include Elizabeth 's husband , Prince Philip , Duke of Edinburgh , as well as Queen Margrethe II of Denmark , King Harald V of Norway , Queen Sofía of Spain and former King Constantine II of Greece -- each of whom is also descended from Queen Victoria ; one of her many cousins is King Juan Carlos I of Spain , also a great-great-grandson of Victoria .  )
